{"type":null,"faqId":19328,"title":"触摸屏失灵","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005703082\"><a name=\"_%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%BB%91%E5%B1%8F\"></a></a><span>操作触摸屏时，请保持手和触摸屏的清洁干燥，否则可能会导致触摸屏无响应。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>若手机正在充电，触摸屏可能受电流影响无法正常响应，请尽量使用标配充电器。若使用标配充电器仍然出现触摸屏无响应的情况，请先停止充电，然后查看触摸屏是否有响应。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>若是在运行个别第三方应用时出现触摸屏无响应的情况，可能是第三方应用与手机不兼容导致的。请卸载该应用或备份重要数据后恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>若在进行不同操作时，每个界面的同一位置都出现无响应现象，可能是系统底层相关驱动异常导致，或者是触摸屏故障或其他不良异常。请携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>华为会在官网发布最新软件版本，请进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm\"><span>华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span>根据型号查询下载；或通过在线升级进行手机软件版本更新，以获得更好的使用体验。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":1,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2469","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608222000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":477,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}